{
  "id": "5d1c176675f16500174f524f",
  "title": "使い物にならない",
  "created": 1562122091,
  "updated": 1562122619,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5d1c176675f16500174f524f",
      "text": "使い物にならない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562122091,
      "updated": 1562122091
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1c176baff09e0000a187c6",
      "text": "「この手法は使い物にならない」という発言があった場合に、それは文字通りの意味ではない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562122091,
      "updated": 1562122107
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1c177aaff09e0000a187ca",
      "text": "「話者はこの手法で[有益な結果]を得たことがない」という意味である。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562122107,
      "updated": 1562122167
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1c1776aff09e0000a187c9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562122102,
      "updated": 1562122102
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1c1776aff09e0000a187c8",
      "text": "この観測事実だけからは「この手法は誰にとっても[有益]な結果をもたらさない」か「[話者の能力不足]」かは判断できない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562122102,
      "updated": 1562122177
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1c176caff09e0000a187c7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562122092,
      "updated": 1562122092
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1c1850aff09e0000b38df5",
      "text": "余談",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562122321,
      "updated": 1562122328
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1c1857aff09e0000b38df6",
      "text": "\tある人Xが「手法Aは役に立たない、手法Bも役に立たない、...」とたくさん「有益な結果を得たことがない」事例を積み重ねることで、結果的にXの能力不足の確かさが高まっていく",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562122328,
      "updated": 1562122406
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1c18b0aff09e0000b38df8",
      "text": "\t\t「手法Aは役に立たない」と発言した時、手法Aを下げる意図があるのだろう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562122417,
      "updated": 1562122537
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1c191daff09e0000b38dfb",
      "text": "\t\tしかし、発言という行為の結果として手法Aではなく自分の評価が下がっていく",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562122526,
      "updated": 1562122528
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1c18f5aff09e0000b38df9",
      "text": "\t\t\t意図と逆の効果、興味深い。[人間のバグ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562122485,
      "updated": 1562122548
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1c1857aff09e0000b38df7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562122328,
      "updated": 1562122328
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1c17c9aff09e0000a187cb",
      "text": "関連",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562122185,
      "updated": 1562122187
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1c17cbaff09e0000a187cd",
      "text": "\t[コミュニケーション能力が低い]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562122187,
      "updated": 1562122194
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1c17caaff09e0000a187cc",
      "text": "\t[過度の一般化]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562122187,
      "updated": 1562122597
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1c1965aff09e0000b38dfd",
      "text": "\t[主語が大きい]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562122598,
      "updated": 1562122602
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1c196baff09e0000b38dfe",
      "text": "\t[自分の失敗は自分の能力以外に原因を求める]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562122603,
      "updated": 1562122619
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1c1971aff09e0000b38dff",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562122610,
      "updated": 1562122610
    }
  ]
}